.TH CLOUDCROSS "1" "September 2018" "CloudCross v1.4.2 for Linux" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
CloudCross \- manual page for CloudCross v1.4.2 for Linux
.SH DESCRIPTION
CloudCross v1.4.2 for Linux
is a opensource program for sync local files with a many cloud storages.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR [ \fB\-\-help\fR ]
Produce help message
.TP
\fB\-v\fR [ \fB\-\-version\fR ]
Display CloudCross version
.TP
\fB\-a\fR [ \fB\-\-auth\fR ]
Request authorization token
.TP
\fB\-p\fR [ \fB\-\-path\fR ] arg
Path to sync directory
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Only detect which files need to be uploaded/downloaded,
without actually performing them.
.TP
\fB\-s\fR [ \fB\-\-list\fR ]
Print remote cloud file list
.TP
\fB\-\-use\-include\fR
Use .include file. Without this option by default use .exclude file.
If these files does'nt exists, they  are ignore
.TP
\fB\-\-prefer\fR arg
Define sync strategy. It can be a one of "remote" or "local". By default it's "local"
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-hidden\fR
Not sync hidden files and folders
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-new\-rev\fR
Do not create new revisions of files, overwrite their instead
.TP
\fB\-\-convert\-doc\fR
Convert office document to Google Doc format when upload
and convert him back when download
.TP
\fB\-\-force\fR arg
Forcing upload or download files. It can be a one of "upload" or "download".
This option overrides \fB\-\-prefer\fR option value.
.TP
\fB\-\-provider\fR arg
Set cloud provider for current sync operation. On this moment this option can be
a "google", "yandex", "mailru", "onedrive" or "dropbox". Default provider is Google Drive
.TP
\fB\-\-login\fR arg
Set login for access to cloud provider.
Now it used only for Cloud Mail.ru
.TP
\fB\-\-password\fR arg
Set password for access to cloud provider.
Now it used only for Cloud Mail.ru
.TP
\fB\-\-http\-proxy\fR arg
Use http proxy server for connection to cloud provider.
<arg> must be in a ip_address_or_host_name:port_number format
.TP
\fB\-\-socks5\-proxy\fR arg
Use socks5 proxy server for connection to cloud provider.
<arg> must be in a ip_address_or_host_name:port_number format
.TP
\fB\-\-cloud\-space\fR
Showing total and free space  of cloud
.TP
\fB\-\-filter\-type\fR
Filter type for .include and .exclude files. Can be set to "regexp" or "wildcard".                               Ignored if it set in files
.TP
\fB\-\-single\-thread\fR
Run as single threaded
.TP
\fB\-\-low\-memory\fR
Reduce memory utilization during reading a remote file list. Using of this                                option may do increase of synchronization time
.TP
\fB\-\-empty\-trash\fR
Delete all files from cloud trash bin.
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-sync\fR
If this option is set synchronization mechanism will be disabled and remote file list                              not be a readed. Local files will be uploaded without consideration of existence                              of this files on remote. Use with carefully
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.B https://cloudcross.mastersoft24.ru/usage
